{
  "texts": [
    "Our evaluation targeted three types of tasks: 100 Construction tasks, 100 Farm-to-table cooking tasks, and 25 Escape room challenges, each executed once.",
    "We terminate a testing round if the task execution exceeds the anticipated time frame or once the task has been successfully completed.",
    "The parameters for LLM reasoning can be found in Appendix 7.",
    "Construction Cooperation Task.",
    "For the construction tasks ranging from 0 to 99, we deployed two agents, Alice and Bob, each equipped with essential APIs, to collaborate effectively."
  ]
}